{"CROQUANTE":[{"def":"A brittle cake or other crisp pastry.","pos":""}],"CROQUET":[{"def":"An open-air game in which two or more players endeavor to drive wooden balls, by means of mallets, through a series of hoops or arches set in the ground according to some pattern.","pos":""},{"def":"The act of croqueting.","pos":""}],"CROQUETTE":[{"def":"A ball of minced meat, fowl, rice, or other ingredients, highly seasoned, and fried.","pos":""}]}